Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.12,0:00:17.53,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Jiki-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.04,0:00:20.79,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Rainbow.{\alpha&HFF&} I want to go there. {Rainbow. I want to go there.(there's no "this one", i think tl misheard "ore" for "kore"}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.79,0:00:23.25,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Rainbow. I want to go there.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.25,0:00:24.92,Default,Na,0,0,0,,It might be Karoku!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.92,0:00:25.50,Default,Na,0,0,0,,I want to go!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.34,0:00:28.80,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.80,0:00:32.80,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a little creepy, almost as if we're being sent an invitation.{actually "invited" feels better than "lured in" here. nothing creepy about being lured in, but everything so if it's "invited"}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.80,0:00:34.47,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.47,0:00:35.05,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.22,0:00:42.14,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,They're so easy to read.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.14,0:00:44.06,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,It's obvious that they don't want us to go near that place.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.28,0:00:56.24,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Gareki-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.83,0:01:02.29,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crate of Thorns!{Yogi's fighting words in German}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.89,0:01:25.44,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous for you, Gareki-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.19,0:01:31.61,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,I'll take you back to the ship right away.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.07,0:01:39.66,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,You're going to where that rainbow is, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.66,0:01:40.53,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.03,0:01:42.12,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,I'm sure over there–
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.12,0:01:44.66,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,I know. I slow you down.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.66,0:01:50.08,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,I haven't been keeping up with your speed at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.17,0:01:55.97,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,I'm such a freaking burden.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.80,0:02:06.35,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Sorry, but can you please take me with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.60,0:02:11.52,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Uh, um, ah, Gareki-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.69,0:02:17.11,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Gareki-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.99,0:02:26.33,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I also wanted you to come with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.37,0:02:31.25,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Let's go save Nai-chan together.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.34,0:02:35.00,Default,Ak,0,0,0,,Azana, you're confused!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.42,0:02:38.63,Default,Ak,0,0,0,,You should be aware that you're talking nonsense!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.51,Default,Az,0,0,0,,We're weak.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.89,0:02:46.52,Default,Az,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}Even Murano who cares so much about the creatures in Vinto
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.52,0:02:49.02,Default,Az,0,0,0,,sought the powers of Varuga.{suggest "sought/turned to the powers of Varuga}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.35,0:02:56.53,Default,Ak,0,0,0,,Were you the one who used my name in order to provide drugs for him?{not forged, but used Akari's name("said his name")}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.53,0:03:01.03,Default,Az,0,0,0,,Everyone trusts your name, Akari-sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.37,0:03:07.45,Default,Az,0,0,0,,I don't want to do anything violent but I want you to come with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.63,0:03:13.79,Default,Ak,0,0,0,,Hirato...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.38,0:03:20.68,Default,Az,0,0,0,,Ak-Akari-sensei, I've very much\N looked up to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.68,0:03:24.10,Default,Az,0,0,0,,Your strong mind... I've always\N admired it... from the shadows...{Your strong mind... I've always admired it... from the shadows...}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.10,0:03:28.14,Default,Az,0,0,0,,But why are you so talented?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.64,Default,Az,0,0,0,,Why do you even exist?!{suggest "even exist" for stronger impact?}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.98,0:03:34.81,Default,Az,0,0,0,,I feel so miserable and hate myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.81,0:03:35.65,Default,Az,0,0,0,,And I hate you as well!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.98,0:03:41.45,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,National Defense Organization, Research Tower, Life Division member, Azana.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.11,0:03:43.91,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Treason's a very serious crime.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.91,0:03:46.70,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,According to regulations,\N I can execute you promptly.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.45,Default,Ak,0,0,0,,Hirato, don't do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.54,0:03:51.25,Default,Ak,0,0,0,,Wait,{\alpha&HFF&} Azana!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.08,Default,Ak,0,0,0,,Wait, Azana!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.13,0:04:04.05,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,We've been letting him run free in order to get concrete evidence.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.26,0:04:11.06,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Ikami will chase him wherever Azana goes.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.44,0:04:16.65,Default,Ak,0,0,0,,Azana...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.30,Default,Va,0,0,0,,Woohoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.85,0:04:48.76,Default,Va,0,0,0,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.72,0:04:52.39,Default,Va,0,0,0,,{\i1}The bug in the last dungeon!{suggest splitting this into "Hey there."(to catch Kiichi's attention) and then next time his skill "Rasdan bug!"}{Split}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.81,0:04:54.02,Default,Ki,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.69,0:04:56.06,Default,Va,0,0,0,,Woohoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.12,0:05:13.00,Default,Ki,0,0,0,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.00,0:05:16.42,Default,Ki,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way, Tsuki-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.84,0:05:20.30,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Kiichi,{\alpha&HFF&} good job.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.30,0:05:21.63,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Kiichi, good job.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.80,0:05:29.89,Default,Ur,0,0,0,,Holding back?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.39,0:05:38.15,Default,Ur,0,0,0,,Banshees continuously adjust the pressure of\N their binds when the target is to be captured alive.{Banshees continuously adjust the pressure of their binds when the target is to be captured alive.}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.90,Default,Ur,0,0,0,,In the current situation,{In the present situation,}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.90,0:05:45.40,Default,Ur,0,0,0,,they're balancing its power in order to prohibit my movements{they're balancing the power in order to prohibit my movements without killing me.}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.40,0:05:47.15,Default,Ur,0,0,0,,without killing me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.15,0:05:54.16,Default,Ur,0,0,0,,But right at that moment, I managed to make a hole underneath my stomach.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.83,0:05:58.29,Default,Ur,0,0,0,,A hole of summoning\Nfor my servants to emerge from.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.21,0:06:00.38,Default,Iv,0,0,0,,Raise the pressure!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.09,0:06:02.25,Default,Ur,0,0,0,,Fools!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.97,Default,Ur,0,0,0,,The balance has already been broken!{I shall break the balance!}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.89,0:06:20.40,Default,Ur,0,0,0,,Trying to capture me by only using remotely controlled banshees...{yes, multiple banshees}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.40,0:06:25.07,Default,Ur,0,0,0,,The Second Ship Captain is taking me pretty lightly, isn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.28,0:06:31.91,Default,Ur,0,0,0,,As we speak, worms of Circus are being attracted to the rainbow's light.{Also, worms of Circus are being attracted to the light from the rainbow.}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.28,0:06:35.83,Default,Ur,0,0,0,,I will exterminate all of you in one go.{I will exterminate all of you in one go.}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.33,Default,Ur,0,0,0,,Your madness ends here.{ikarete?}{*skip first}{come back}{Suggest just combining 70-71 with the sentence just being "I will exterminate all of you in one go."}{Come back to this scene for the patch after FUNimation release}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.59,Default,Iv,0,0,0,,I should be the one saying that!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.84,0:06:43.67,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.67,0:06:44.92,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.85,0:06:57.89,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.64,0:07:01.90,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,Hey, that's confusing.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.40,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,You cracked your whip so hard!{You cracked your whip so hard...}{suggesting alternative}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.40,0:07:05.11,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,It was a close call!{It was a close call!}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.57,0:07:06.28,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Yogi!{\alpha&HFF&} Gareki!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.07,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Yogi! Gareki!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.03,0:07:08.82,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.11,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Nai-chan.{I added the ~ because he's like Nai-chaaaannn (Remove it if you want for a period xD. Editor choice)}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.82,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Aren't you scared? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.82,0:07:14.08,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,Don't lower your guard.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.41,0:07:17.70,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,The bottom of the rainbow is over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.04,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Karoku...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.72,0:07:35.10,Default,Va,0,0,0,,Would you like to sleep with a mother's embrace?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.47,0:07:41.77,Default,Va,0,0,0,,I'll give you eternal slumber before the door is closed.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.61,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a time limit?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.19,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Jiki-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.45,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,I'll take care of things here.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.99,0:07:53.78,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.03,0:08:33.95,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,That is…{I usually combine "That is" -> That's but this sounds better with just "That is..."}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.17,0:08:45.79,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Yogi!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.59,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crate of Thorns!{Yogi's fighting words-German}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.97,0:08:58.89,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Iva!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.27,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Tsukumo-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.60,0:09:05.31,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Run, Nai!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.27,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let us make it.{\alpha&HFF&} Let us make it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.27,0:09:09.65,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let us make it. Let us make it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.53,0:09:19.62,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,Find your way here by following the calm sound of flowing air.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.58,0:09:23.45,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,This is the inside of a large shell.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.45,0:09:28.38,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,Even the minuscule sounds of flapping wings will multiply and echo beautifully.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.34,0:09:34.88,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,Even if it's a space where there's nothing but emptiness, if you go there, a miracle will happen. {Even if it's a space where there's nothing but emptiness, If you go there, a miracle will happen.}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.85,0:09:40.35,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Give me the key to the door!{think should be "the key"}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.26,0:09:46.10,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,If you don't, I'll take your head off at this very moment!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.36,0:09:55.28,Default,Ur,0,0,0,,Impatient members of Circus,{members of circus or people of circus}{Impatient people of Circus,(to me it seemed like this is what he's saying, and also based on Yogi's prior reaction)}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.28,0:09:56.91,Default,Ur,0,0,0,,this situation right now...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.91,0:09:58.99,Default,Ur,0,0,0,,It is a box of secrets for us as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.37,0:10:03.24,Default,Ur,0,0,0,,It can only be opened from the inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.83,0:10:04.79,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,What are you–?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.52,0:10:33.27,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Nai.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.24,0:10:37.65,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Karoku.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.75,0:10:47.91,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Karoku!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.46,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,Nai.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.46,0:10:56.59,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Karoku, you're alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.59,0:10:57.59,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Your wounds...{\alpha&HFF&} are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.59,0:10:58.30,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Your wounds... are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.88,0:11:02.30,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's Karoku?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.14,0:11:06.52,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rather, where the heck is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.89,0:11:11.94,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Nai. Someone is lying on the ground.{Hey, Nai. Something is lying on the ground.}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.81,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are you ignoring–?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.82,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't move my body.{suggest splitting this}{Split}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.74,0:11:21.20,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Say, can I give this to Gareki?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.32,0:11:26.20,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Work, my voice!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.91,0:11:27.08,Alt,Na,0,0,0,,I promised him when he saved my life.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.08,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}My voice!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.71,0:11:31.00,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Nai!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.04,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Something's wrong,{\alpha&HFF&} you fool!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.50,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Something's wrong, you fool!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.21,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Karoku?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.63,0:11:39.92,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Karoku!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.22,0:11:42.30,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\1}Huh? That's Karoku?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.72,0:11:45.80,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Blood. There's lots of blood.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.14,0:11:49.85,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,I wanted him to see you for one last time.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.85,0:11:53.94,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,I spoke for his wish and called you, Nai.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.94,0:11:55.81,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,To come right away.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.07,0:12:00.07,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,He was happy to be able to see you again, Nai.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.45,0:12:06.58,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,In fact, his time should've ended in a place of emptiness.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.41,0:12:11.00,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,I'm happy to see you for the first time,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.00,0:12:14.50,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,since we've only talked so far.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.34,0:12:21.59,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,But the part of Karoku who had lived with you at Niji forest is also now inside me.{But the part of Karoku who had lived with you at Niji Forest is also now inside me.}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.76,0:12:24.72,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,I am now Karoku,{\alpha&HFF&} Nai.{I am now Karoku, Nai.}{added now for emphasis}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.72,0:12:25.59,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,I am now Karoku, Nai.{I am now Karoku, Nai.}{added now for emphasis}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.47,0:12:30.52,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,You wouldn't wear old clothes you can't use anymore, would you?{You would not continue wearing old clothes you can't use anymore, would you?}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.52,0:12:33.23,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,It's the same thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.23,0:12:34.98,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,Did I surprise you?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.31,0:12:37.90,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,Come with me, Nai.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.48,0:12:41.19,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,You're such a good boy for coming all the way here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.19,0:12:44.41,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,It's natural for you to be on this side of the world.{It is natural for you to be in this side of the world.(within this space or outside the world i think?)}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.07,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.07,0:12:47.70,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rise, my arm!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.70,0:12:50.16,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,You should properly say good-bye to Gareki-kun. {maybe rewording?}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.87,0:12:53.96,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,You can't stay with him forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.29,0:12:57.08,Default,Na,0,0,0,,I don't want to. You're different.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.50,0:13:02.17,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,Nai, you're being difficult.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.72,0:13:06.55,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,If I break Gareki-kun, there would be nothing to hold you back anymore, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.80,0:13:07.80,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.05,0:13:09.05,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.02,0:13:19.27,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad. His pulse is…
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.36,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.82,0:13:27.28,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,If you need to play more, I'll wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.99,0:13:30.24,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,I have a big heart, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.70,0:13:31.37,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,Nai.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.97,0:13:48.64,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,Go and play as much as you want.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.05,0:13:52.14,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Launching an attack without our authorization.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.81,0:13:55.27,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Are you aware of how much confusion was created in order to clean up the mess
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.27,0:13:58.19,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,due to what you have done, Circus?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.19,0:14:00.65,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,This incident was ordered by me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.65,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,I will take full responsibility.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.65,0:14:07.15,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,All the same, I should share part of the blame for supporting the attack.{All the same, I should share the responsibility for supporting the attack.}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.41,0:14:11.95,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,I'm aware of what we have done, but I would also like you to look at our results.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.33,0:14:15.50,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Results? Who are you kidding?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.50,0:14:18.46,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,You couldn't even catch sight of Palnedo.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.46,0:14:22.96,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,And that Palnedo is claiming that everything this time was all masterminded by Uro without his knowledge{And that Palned is claiming that everything this time was all masterminded by Uro without his knowledge}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.96,0:14:25.59,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,and that he is innocent.{Alt line: and is expressing his own innocence}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.59,0:14:28.30,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,On top of that, you also failed to capture Uro. {Alt line: On top of that, you couldn't even capture Uro.}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.30,0:14:33.10,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Furthermore, Azana,\Nwho is accused of treason, is also missing!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.10,0:14:38.10,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,By the way, how is Karoku, the person reported as your rescue target?{By the way, how is Karoku, the person reported as your rescue target?}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.90,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Karoku was brought in with the condition of cardiac arrest.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.90,0:14:44.86,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,He was revived by the treatment received by Doctor Akari.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.11,0:14:48.15,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,But has yet to regain consciousness.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.49,0:14:53.74,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Karoku...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.87,0:15:01.29,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Nai-kun. Let's go back to the ship for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.71,0:15:03.63,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.05,0:15:10.38,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Answer me!{Answer me!(this dakara is just something like a forceful exclamation)}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.05,0:15:15.89,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,I'm asking if there's any special way to enter, like taking a test,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.89,0:15:18.39,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,even if I don't have a family register?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.73,0:15:21.10,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,You mean the government's School?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.10,0:15:23.23,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,What do you want to study there?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.90,0:15:31.28,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,I really hate the Varugas and Kafka and all those guys...{I totally loathe Varuga and Kafka.}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.91,0:15:36.33,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,They killed both Tsubaki and Yotaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.33,0:15:39.79,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,They made Tsubame and Nai cry a lot.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.67,0:15:43.21,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,I feel so upset about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.13,0:15:57.35,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,At first, I thought if I stayed here, I could have my revenge on Kafka some day.{At first, I thought if I stayed here, I could have my revenge on Kafka some day.}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.35,0:16:04.31,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,But I felt so uncool just staying around without being of any help at all.{But I felt so uncool just staying around without being useful at all.}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.77,0:16:08.99,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,That's why I want to learn new techniques and get some credentials.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.99,0:16:10.57,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,And one day be able to beat Varuga.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.40,0:16:16.20,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Then I'll be able to... stay here with my head up.{Then I will be able to... stay with you guys with my head up.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey–
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.58,0:16:20.29,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,I'm saying I want to make this my job!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.29,0:16:22.42,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Why are you so excited all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.42,0:16:24.46,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,I've been patiently listening to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.46,0:16:26.88,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,I've researched many books
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.88,0:16:31.05,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,but not a single one mentioned on how a person without a family register could get into school.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.05,0:16:32.30,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.97,0:16:36.14,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll get you tossed in there.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.47,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Into the School.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.26,0:16:42.48,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,However, my responsibility for dragging you around stops there.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.02,0:16:47.32,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Any results beyond that point\Nwill be entirely up to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.32,0:16:48.48,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,It's not that easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.32,0:16:54.70,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,I look forward to finding out if you will come back to our world.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.32,0:16:58.87,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Such results are obvious!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.76,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,So he's not here...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.05,0:17:15.30,Default,Yogi,0,0,0,,Before we went to the Smoky Mansion,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.97,Default,Yogi,0,0,0,,he talked with Hirato-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yukkin
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.35,0:17:22.27,Default,Na,0,0,0,,No way. I want everyone to be here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.85,0:17:25.06,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Everyone together...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.23,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Nai-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.23,0:17:29.82,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Yogi...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.61,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,I guess we should be happy,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.78,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,as it's what Gareki-kun himself has chosen...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.07,0:17:40.91,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,When Gareki-kun asked me what it meant to be a child of the Second Ship,{means or meant?}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.91,0:17:43.04,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,I became awfully worried.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.71,0:17:49.67,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,I mean, to the world we don't really exist, right?{he's saying based on records and knowledge of normal ppl, they're supposed to be dead/not exist at all}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.30,0:17:52.51,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,When I joined Circus,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.51,0:17:54.42,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,in order not to endanger my family,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.76,0:17:57.30,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,and at the same time not let me be shackled down by that,{that -fear of endangering family}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.30,0:17:59.60,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,both my family register and data were modified.{or should I just use "changed"...}{Either works}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.31,0:18:04.43,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,This is the only place I can call home.{lit;this is the only place I can go home to}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.89,0:18:06.85,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,I meet lots of people outside,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.85,0:18:08.44,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,but even if I became friendly with them,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.94,0:18:12.02,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,in the end everyone would say good-bye and move on.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.69,0:18:15.44,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.70,0:18:20.20,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,When Nai-chan and Gareki-kun came here,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.49,0:18:22.70,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,I was very happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.04,0:18:26.25,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,It felt like a breath of fresh air from outside,{into the ship}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.71,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,and I was so excited.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.42,0:18:34.51,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,But now for Gareki-kun, he will go through many things,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.51,0:18:38.80,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,and meet many people whom he would hold dear out there.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.80,0:18:39.93,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.42,Default,Nai(bg),0,0,0,,Gareki!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.42,Alt,Yo(bg),0,0,0,,Gareki-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.38,0:19:18.01,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,You guys...{or "Guys"? "Everyone"?}{I think the first one fits better}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.01,0:19:21.05,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Gareki-kun... um...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.39,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Gareki...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.39,0:19:24.85,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,You mustn't cry.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.81,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Gareki-kun would feel awkward.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.85,0:19:29.56,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Gareki-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.73,0:19:34.07,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Think of him as me, and talk to him whenever you're having a hard time...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.07,0:19:37.19,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,You mean you talk to this thing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.19,0:19:38.86,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Gareki-kun, um...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.86,0:19:39.78,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.49,0:19:45.16,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,I-I'm still bad at this,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.20,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,but I made this with Nai-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.62,0:19:49.41,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,A Niji plushy...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.41,0:19:51.08,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Think of this as Nai-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.21,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's kind of ugly
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.21,0:19:53.96,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}and awfully deformed...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.42,0:19:57.34,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.34,0:19:58.71,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Gareki...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.38,0:20:00.22,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.81,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Karoku... is still asleep, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.35,0:20:09.22,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.22,0:20:12.98,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Then make sure you ask him before we meet again.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.31,0:20:15.65,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,That if it's okay to give me that.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.65,0:20:19.57,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll keep on calling out to Karoku.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.24,0:20:24.24,Alt,Yo,0,0,0,,Gareki-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.24,0:20:24.24,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Gareki!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.49,0:20:28.95,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,What shall I do if we never meet again?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.95,0:20:29.54,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Yogi!{\alpha&HFF&} Nai-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.54,0:20:30.25,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Yogi! Nai-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.25,0:20:32.12,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.12,0:20:33.75,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,After all...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.75,0:20:35.04,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.04,0:20:36.04,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.96,0:20:43.51,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,So you guys think I wouldn't be able to get my credentials and come back here?{all the way till "omaera"}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.51,0:20:44.13,Default,Na+Yo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.68,0:20:46.76,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Don't you want me to come back?{Lit:Is it so bad for me to come back?}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.76,0:20:47.85,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.85,0:20:49.14,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.14,0:20:52.02,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Credentials for... what?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.02,0:20:54.27,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear anything from that shitty four-eyes?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.48,0:20:56.48,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Hirato...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.48,0:20:58.27,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Did he do this on purpose?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.77,0:21:01.28,Default,Yo+Na,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.49,0:21:04.91,Default,Iv,0,0,0,,You really have a horrible personality.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.03,0:21:10.79,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,Hirato-san, the reason you pay so much attention to Gareki-kun is
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.79,0:21:13.00,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,because he was in that ship, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.79,Default,Ki,0,0,0,,What ship?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.79,0:21:16.79,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,That Kafka research lab ship.{he's saying Kafka's "experiement" ship}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.55,Default,Ki,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.55,0:21:23.34,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,It was just the right timing for Gareki, who escaped death from that ship,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.34,0:21:26.80,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,when he met Nai, who from that chance meeting, led Gareki all the way here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.26,0:21:30.52,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Something like a miraculous encounter, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.14,0:21:35.31,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,It feels like everything just mysteriously came together.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.73,0:21:42.03,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,It could be that Nai's very existence attracts the inevitable to happen..
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.08,0:21:58.83,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.46,0:22:04.80,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.39,0:22:18.69,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Gareki, you have become warm!{Gareki... has become warm!}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.69,0:22:19.69,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.78,0:22:28.70,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Good-bye,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:29.12,0:22:30.20,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,you dumb animal!
